Valencia

ValenciaESVLCport

GenoaITGOAport

Jona

The cheapest way to ship cargo from Valencia, Spain to Jona, Switzerland is to deliver by truck from Valencia to Valencia port, transfer to vessel and ship to Genoa port, then deliver by road to final destination in Jona. The route's total transit time is estimated at around 10 days, including loading and unloading operations at origin and destination as well as terminal handling at transit terminals.

The most environmentally friendly shipping method from Valencia, Spain to Jona, Switzerland is to deliver by truck from Valencia to Silla rail yard, transfer to wagon and deliver by rail to Rekingen rail yard, then deliver by road to final destination in Jona.
